{"tid":2126584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"70歲譚詠麟刪IG Facebook 「斬腳趾」避網民日日轟炸","createTime":"2020-07-27T02:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:55:01.000Z","uid":44730,"like":249,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4e1b35527e9d4f3db35f14f54d760547a1eb5b","tid":2126584,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fGMFcMRtsWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfGMFcMRtsWk&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qxyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=787f8a6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fGMFcMRtsWk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"teal\">冇咗班忠粉多咗好多小粉紅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n事實，兩年前開始玩IG、Facebook的阿倫，自從現身撐警活動後，日日都被大量網民洗版式留言鬧爆，圈中一直出名人緣好的他自然無癮到極點，無能力阻止網民，當事人唯有斬腳趾避沙蟲，日前，他索性刪除玩了2年的IG及Facebook fans page，跟過萬粉絲斬纜，冇眼屎乾淨盲！現在只玩微博的阿倫，雖然冇咗一班香港忠粉，下個月23日就奔七的阿倫，就多了內地小粉紅支持。"},{"pid":"fdb96173b40b5ee51a81c964af27ce6484c3d68e","tid":2126584,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">飽到肚凸凸</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對於阿倫，相信最重要得身邊人支持。疫情雖嚴峻，向來愛吃的阿倫，這天被發現跟Wendy和兩位跟隨了超過三十年的助手飯聚傾公事。四人邊食邊傾，阿倫明顯心情回復正指數，離開食肆，阿倫在等車期間又突然興之所至，拿出手機玩自拍，兩位助手亦十分配合，在旁幫手打燈，完成在黑暗中拍照一事。"},{"pid":"dade36fa5a7b2713c5c67e41c4edfe07138dcaf9","tid":2126584,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"teal\">同Wendy心有靈犀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於紅顏知己Wendy，替阿倫誕下兒子譚曉風後，親密關係開始浮面，去年阿倫因表明撐警立場，加上疫情爆發，以致今年年初的10場溫拿演唱會被逼取消，之後就被拍到Wendy陪去拜佛及到坪洲散心，有這位由歌迷開始成為紅顏知己的忠粉撐住，暫刪ig和Facebook fans page的阿倫，算是有些少安慰。看兩人心有靈犀，候車時不約而留意到一隻可愛的「閃燈狗」，70歲阿倫之「苦」，相信最清楚的一定是Wendy。"},{"pid":"6b66cb5d31d8ef50c86267e7f0d98bcca2b0ed0b","tid":2126584,"uid":53498,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"七張就買定棺材啦"},{"pid":"eb1ed08ab1557f31a7f981b4f137d539d9c33d2f","tid":2126584,"uid":300782,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba4a34ada4aae5a74cdb628e610019676d6c956","tid":2126584,"uid":288675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"小粉紅都係要政苦養..."},{"pid":"0e16c92474e36326aa6d6af0e39fb7bb5bf0fbae","tid":2126584,"uid":44730,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"navy\">藍校長</span></strong></span> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f01b7ce2cc6c74fea32a94c236aa68f2c53f2681","tid":2126584,"uid":272652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"玩微博囉"},{"pid":"fd6f7df835eb7b2ad7b3c0263dd6441242e3a8cf","tid":2126584,"uid":7922,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"倫伯幾時頭七?<br />\n<br />\n到時得番小粉紅歌迷送行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d2e3edcdd2885eca5776b706f4afcfa85bd37","tid":2126584,"uid":156130,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"奔七的阿倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef22927e0d939321dfd5c79e26f28784ce4e340b","tid":2126584,"uid":50101,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"這陷阱這陷阱這陷阱"},{"pid":"4544cfe64776b96f3909852d6c507897e6804b4e","tid":2126584,"uid":177630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/fac